🎮 Game
Name: Worldfall
Genre: Adventure, Exploration, Survival, Story, Co-op, Sci‑Fi, Open World
Players: 1--4
📖 Story
Scientists discover an Ancient Energy. During research, corruption spreads across the world. The scientist who later becomes the King secretly experiments on himself to become stronger. Realizing the danger, he briefly suppresses the infection and hides the Ancient Energy into multiple fragments around the world before losing control. Governments collapse, humanity falls, and survivors gather in underground bunkers. The player's journey is to survive, uncover the truth, and decide humanity's future.
👑 Endings
Kill the King (virus continues, army collapses)
Save the King and destroy the source
Future chapters continue after the ending
